/*!-----------------------------------------------------------------------
 |	ws_vars/3
 |	ws_vars(WS, ARCH_OS, WSHeaderLines)
 |	ws_vars(+, +, -)
 |
 |	- list makefile window system vars/header lines for an arch/os combination
 *-----------------------------------------------------------------------*/
